Recycling share1=IF THEN ELSE( Processing inflow > 0 , "Flow Recycling SDMFA (Secondary input)"\
		 / Processing inflow, 0 )
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

"Use Gap SD-MFA to MFA (%)"=(Use DMFA - Use SDMFA) / Use DMFA * 100
	~	
	~		|

"Recycling Gap SD-MFA to MFA (%)"=(Recycling DMFA-Recycling SDMFA)/Recycling DMFA*100
	~	
	~		|

"Primary input Gap SD-MFA to MFA (%)"=(Primary input DMFA-Primary input SDMFA)/Primary input DMFA\
		*100
	~	
	~		|

Flow WM to Recycling=MIN(Recyclable waste SDMFA * Recycling Fraction , Recycling Capacity SDMFA\
		 )
	~	ton/Year
	~	Actual recycling flow in SD-MFA, constrained by recycling capacity and \
		effective recyclable waste.
	|

Primary input SD=MAX(0, Demand*Demand index - Secondary input)
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

Potential Fab to Use=Demand*Demand index*Use Fraction
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

Flow Fab to Use=Demand*Demand index*Use Fraction
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

Total Mass Balance SD= INTEG (Demand*Demand index - Demand,
		0)
	~	ton
	~	Cumulative physical feasibility gap in SD. Negative values indicate \
		economically driven demand exceeds the baseline material availability \
		represented by DMFA.
	~	:SUPPLEMENTARY 
	|

Recycling share=IF THEN ELSE( Primary input SD+"Flow Recycling SD (secondary input)" \
		> 0 , "Flow Recycling SD (secondary input)"
	 / (Primary input SD+"Flow Recycling SD (secondary input)"
	) , 0 )
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Processing=Demand*Demand index
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

Fab to WM SD=Demand*Demand index*Scrap Fraction
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

WM to Disposal SD=Total WM SD-Flow WM to Recycling SD
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

Total WM SD=Fab to WM SD+Flow use to WM
	~	ton/Year
	~	Total waste generated in the SD model before applying the effective scrap \
		recycling availability.
	|

Flow WM to Disposal SD=WM to Disposal SD
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

Flow WM to Recycling SD=MIN ( Recycling capacity SD , Recyclable waste SD*Recycling fraction SD\
		 )
	~	ton/Year
	~	Actual recycling flow in the SD model, constrained by recycling capacity \
		and effective recyclable waste.
	|

Total Waste to Management SD=Fabrication waste SD+Flow use to WM
	~	ton/Year
	~	Total waste generated in the SD model, including fabrication scrap and \
		end-of-life waste.
	|

Fabrication waste SD=Demand*Demand index*Scrap Fraction
	~	ton/Year
	~	Fabrication scrap generated in the SD model.
	|

SDMFA material availability target=0.95
	~	Dmnl
	~	Long-run material availability constraint for SD-MFA.
	|

SDMFA material availability adjustment time=5
	~	Year
	~	Delay before the material constraint becomes fully binding, so primary \
		input starts from the same baseline as other models.
	|

WM Balance=WM- (Waste management to disposal+Waste management to Recycling
	)
	~	ton/Year
	~		~	:SUPPLEMENTARY 
	|

Waste management to disposal=WM-Waste management to Recycling
	~	ton/Year
	~	Residual waste to landfill after actual recycling.
	|

Seconddary input DMFA="Flow Recyling DMFA (Secondary input)"
	~	
