Profitability=Market price-Production cost
	~	$/ton
	~		|

WM to Disposal=Total Waste to Management-Flow WM to Recycling
	~	ton/Year
	~		|

Base market price=2
	~	$/ton
	~	Harga pasar normal (tanpa intervensi kebijakan / subsidi / recycling).
		Dipakai untuk menghitung indeks harga:
		
		Price_Index = Market_Price / Base_Market_Price
		Sehingga model tahu apakah harga:
			•	lebih mahal dari normal → konsumsi turun
			•	lebih murah dari normal → konsumsi naik
	|

Base virgin cost=1.6
	~	$/ton
	~	Biaya produksi bila 100% bahan baku virgin (non-recycled).
		Ini menggambarkan:
			•	harga resin plastik virgin
			•	harga energi
			•	harga bahan baku kimia
		Ini menjadi baseline untuk menghitung penurunan biaya akibat peningkatan \
		recycled share.
	|

Base virgin cost1=
	1.6
	~	$/ton
	~		|

Demand index=SMOOTHI( MAX( 0.85 , MIN( 1.25 , 1 - (Price index - 1) * Price sensitivity\
		 ) ),
		Demand adjustment time,
		1)
	~	Dmnl
	~	Smoothed demand response to price change. Initial value is 1 so demand \
		starts from baseline and only changes after recycling affects secondary \
		supply and price.
	|

Demand index1=SMOOTHI( MAX( 0.85 , MIN( 1.2 , 1 - (Price index1 - 1) * Price sensitivity1\
		 ) ),
		Demand adjustment time,
		1)
	~	Dmnl
	~	Smoothed demand response to price change for SD-MFA. Initial value is 1 so \
		smelting inflow starts from baseline demand.
	|

Demand adjustment time=5
	~	Year
	~	Delay in consumption response to material price changes.
	|

Desired recycling capacity SD=Recyclable waste SD*Recycling fraction SD
	~	ton/Year
	~	Target recycling capacity follows effective recyclable waste, with \
		fabrication scrap availability applied consistently.
	|

Desired recycling capacity SDMFA=Recyclable waste SDMFA*Recycling Fraction
	~	ton/Year
	~	Target recycling capacity for SD-MFA follows effective recyclable waste \
		while preserving material balance.
	|

Recycling capacity adjustment time=10
	~	Year
	~	Delay for recycling capacity to approach desired capacity.
	|

Depreciation fabrication=Depreciation rate*Fabrication capacity SD
	~	1/Year
	~		|

Depreciation of Recycling=Depreciation rate of Rec*Recycling Capacity SDMFA
	~	1/Year
	~		|

Depreciation rate=
	0.05
	~	Year
	~		|

Depreciation rate of Rec=0.06
	~	Year
	~		|

Depreciation rate recycling=0.06
	~	Year
	~	Tingkat penurunan kapasitas recycling karena aging, maintenance, teknologinya cepat \
		berubah.
		
		Interpretasi waktu pakai
		
		Umur fasilitas recycling ≈ 1 / 0.06 ≈ 16.7 tahun
		Lebih pendek dari pabrik fabrikasi, karena fasilitas recycling lebih \
		sering diganti/upgrade.
	|

